Welcome to my homepage! 

I'm currently a 5th year phd student in the [https://statistics.yale.edu/ Statistics and Data Science] at Yale University, advised by Professor [http://www.stat.yale.edu/~zf59/ Zhou Fan]. I am also very fortunate to be supervised by Professors [https://sites.google.com/site/xiaohongchenyale/ Xiaohong Chen], [https://sahandnegahban.com/ Sahand Negahban], [https://yisun.io/ Yi Sun], [https://sites.stat.washington.edu/people/fanghan/ Fang Han] and [https://sites.google.com/view/bcaffo/home Brian Caffo] on particular projects.

Prior to joining Yale, I received my Bachelor's degree in mathematics and statistics from the [http://www.math.pku.edu.cn/ School of Mathematical Sciences] and a dual degree in Economics from the [http://www.nsd.pku.edu.cn/ China Center for Economic Research] at [http://english.pku.edu.cn/ Peking University].


